<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN329-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai. maturai aṟuvai vāṇikaṉ iḷavēṭṭaṉār.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en" type="translation">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="PN329">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>illaṭu kaḷḷiṉ cilkuṭic cīṟūrp</l>
<l>puṭainaṭu kalli ṉāṭpali yūṭṭi</l>
<l>naṉṉī rāṭṭi neynnaṟaik koḷīi</l>
<l>maṅkuṉ māppukai maṟukuṭaṉ kamaḻu</l>
<l>marumuṉai yirukkait tāyiṉum varimiṭaṟ</l>
<l>ṟaravuṟai puṟṟat taṟṟē nāḷum</l>
<l>puravalar puṉka ṇōkkā tiravalark</l>
<l>karukā tīyum vaṇmai</l>
<l>yuraicā ṉeṭuntakai yōmpu mūrē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Even though it is a seat on the difficult frontier,</l>
<l>where the streets all are fragrant with dark smoke in a cloud</l>
<l>after kindling the fragrance with ghee, having splashed good water,</l>
<l>feeding a daily offering to the stone set up on the side</l>
<l>of the little village with few home with toddy distilled in the houses,</l>
<l>it is like a termite hill in which a snake with striped throat stays,</l>
<l>the village protected by him who is greatly befitting, worthy of praise</l>
<l>for [his] generosity that gives unstintingly</l>
<l>to mendicants without looking at the sorrow of those protected by him.   </l>
</lg>
    </div>
